Meta Companies
and where the
data centers
we rely on are located and externally with our Third-Party Service Providers. We carry out necessary transfers outside the European Economic Area, including to the United States and other countries to:
operate and provide our Services. We also allow you to share information and connect with your family and friends around the globe; and
allow us to fix, analyse and improve our Services.
